Scotland Decides: Salmond versus Darling

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Glenn Campbell, published by BBC in 2014 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

As Scotland prepares to vote on the biggest decision in 300 years, join Glenn Campbell and a specially-invited audience live in the iconic Kelvingrove Art Gallery and Museum in Glasgow, as Alex Salmond and Alistair Darling lay out their competing visions for the future of the country. This is round 2.

